Description: dominatR is an R package for quantifying and visualizing feature dominance in datasets.  dominatR makes use of entropy-based triangular projections and compositional comparison metrics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/VanBortleLab/dominatR, https://vanbortlelab.github.io/dominatR/
